name: Zuzalu Muse dinner
description:
The Zuzalu Muse dinners are an evening of connection and conversation. You will be paired with a fellow Zuzalian, who you have not previously met. Then, you will follow a conversation menu which will guide you through interesting topics, deep reflections, and fun explorations of each other's lives, past, present and future.

On the day of the dinner, you will be sent a secret code word. When you arrive, you must find your match by sharing your code word with them.

Dinner can be at Kiki's, or at any other restaurant. You will have to pay for your own dinner - we can't afford to get this one for you.

To attend, please RSVP at https://airtable.com/shrbXk7IPjygyYsbd
